Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing). Additionally, the paper involves mathematical analysis and algorithm design, which are also relevant to sub-categories such as cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.LG (Machine Learning).
